hadiths[22]{hadithnumber,text}:
6918,jab ( sura Al-Anaam ki) ye aayat ( الذين آمنوا ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظلم‏ ( utri ''jo log eman laey aur unhon-ne eman ko gunah se aalud nahi kya (yani zulm se) '' to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ko bahut nagawar guzri wo kehney lagey bhala ham mein se kon aisa hai jisne eman ke sath koi zulm (yani gunah ( na kya ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is aayat mein zulm se gunah murad nahi hai (balke shirk murad hai) kya tum ne luqman (Alaihissalam) ka qaul nahi suna ( إن الشرك لظلم عظيم‏ ( '' shirk bada zulm hai'' .
6919,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke badey se bada gunah Allah Taala ke sath shirk karna hai aur maan-baap ko sataanaa (unki nafarmani karna (aur jhooti gawahi denaa, teen baar yahi farmaya ya yun farmaya aur jhoot bolnaa barabar baar-baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yahi farmatey rahe yahan tak ke ham ne aarzoo ki ke kash! aap khamosh ho jatey."
6920,aik ganwaar (naam naa-maaloom) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya kehney lagaa: ya Rasulullah! badey badey gunah kon se hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke sath shirk karnaa.'' us ne puchha phir kon sa gunaah? aap ne farmaya ''maan-baap ko sataanaa.'' puchha : phir kon sa? aap ne farmaya ''(ghamoos) qism khaanaa.'' Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! (ghamoos) qism kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jaan-bojh kar kisi musalman ka maal mar leney ke liye jhooti qism khaanaa.''
6921,aik shakhs (naam naa-maaloom) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham ne jo gunah (Islam laney se pahley) jahiliyat ke zamane mein kiye hain kya unka muaakhza ham se hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs Islam ki haalat mein nek aamaal karta raha us se jahiliyat ke gunahon ka muaakhza na hoga ( Allah Taala maaf kar dega (aur jo shakhs musalman ho kar bhi burey kaam karta raha us se donon zamanon ke gunahon ka muaakhza hoga.''
6922,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas kuchh be-deen log laey gaey. aap ne unko jalwaa diya. ye khabar Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko pahunchi to unhon-ne kaha agar main Hakim hota to unko kabhi na jalwaata (doosri tarah se saza deta ( kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aag mein jalaaney se mana farmaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aag Allah ka azab hai tum Allah ke azab se kisi ko mat azab do. main unko qatl karwaa daalta kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai jo shakhs apna Deen badal daley Islam se phir jaey usko qatl kar dalo .
6923,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya mere sath ash'ar qabeeley ke 2 log they ( naam naa-maaloom ( aik mere daahiney taraf tha, doosra baain taraf . us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) miswak kar rahe they. donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ohde ki darkhaast ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abu-Musa ya Abdullah-bin-Qais ! ( rawi ko shak hai) maine usi waqt arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! us parwardigar ki qism jisne aapko sachcha paighambar bana kar bhejaa. unhon-ne apne dil ki baat mujh se nahi kahi thi aur mujh ko malum nahi tha ke ye donon shakhs ohda chahtey hain. abu-Musa kehtey hain jaisey main us waqt aap ki miswak ko dekh raha hun wo aap ke hont ke nichey uthi hui thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo koi ham se ohde ki darkhaast karta hai ham usko ohda nahi detey. lekin abu-Musa ya Abdullah-bin Qais! to Yaman ki hukumat par ja ( khair abu-Musa rawaana huey) iske baad aap ne Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi unke peechhey rawaana kya. jab Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman mein abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas pahunchey to abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke baithney ke liye gaddaa bichhwaayaa aur kehney lagey sawari se utro gaddey par baitho. us waqt unke paas aik shakhs tha ( naam naa-maaloom ( jiski mashkein kasii hui thin. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ye kon shakhs hai? unhon-ne kaha ye Yahudi tha phir musalman hua ab phir Yahudi ho gaya hai aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ajii tum sawari par se utar kar baitho . unhon-ne kaha, main nahi baithtaa jab tak Allah aur uske rasool ke hukm ke muwafiq ye qatl na kya jaeyga teen baar yahi kaha, aakhir abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya wo qatl kya gaya. phir Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) baithey. ab donon ne raat ki ibadat ( tahajjud guzari (ka zikr chheda . Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main to raat ko ibadat bhi karta hun aur sota bhi hon aur mujhey ummeed hai ke soney mein bhi mujh ko wahi sawab milega jo Namaz padhney aur ibadat karne mein."
6924,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa baney aur Arab ke kuchh log kaafir ban gaey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha tum un logon se kaisey lado gey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to ye farmaya hai mujh ko logon se ladney ka us waqt tak hukm hua jab tak wo la ilaaha-illallaah na kahin phir jisne la ilaaha-illallaah keh liya us ne apne maal aur apni jaan ko mujh se bacha liya albatta kisi haq ke badla uski jaan ya maal ko nuqsan pahunchaya jaey to ye aur baat hai. ab iske dil mein kya hai iska hisab leney wala Allah hai.
6925,"main to Allah ki qism us shakhs se ladunga jo Namaz aur zakat mein farq karey, isliye ke zakat maal ka haq hai) jaisey Namaz jism ka haq hai) Allah ki qism ! agar ye log mujh ko aik bakri ka bachcha na dengey jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko diya kartey they, to main uske na dene par unse ladunga. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha qism Allah ki iske baad mein samajh gaya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke dil mein jo ladai ka irada hua hai ye Allah ne unke dil mein daala hai aur main pehchan gaya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki raey haq hai."
6926,"aik Yahudi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se guzra kehney laga ( السام عليك‏) yani tum maro. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab mein sirf ( وعليك‏ Mina . Mina ( kaha (to bhi marey ga ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke tum ko malum hua, us ne kya kaha ? us ne ( السام عليك‏ . Mina ( kaha, sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ( hukm ho to ( usko mar daalein . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, nahi. jab kitab waley yahood aur nasara tum ko salam kya karein to tum bhi yahi kaha karo) Waalekum ( ."
6927,yahood mein se chand logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaney ki ijazat chahi jab aaey to kehney lagey ( السام عليك‏ . Mina ( maine jawab mein yun kaha ( عليكم السام واللعنة‏ . Mina ( . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Aaisha ! Allah Taala narmii karta hai aur har kaam mein narmii ko pasand karta hai. maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap ne unka kehna nahi suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine bhi to jawab de diya ( Waalekum ( .
6928,"maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''yahoodii log jab tum musalmanon mein se kisi ko salam kartey hain to (سام عليك‏) kehtey hain tum bhi jawab main ( عليك ( kaha karo."
6929,jaisey mein (is waqt) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh raha hun aap aik paighambar ( Nuh (Alaihissalam) ( ki hikaayat bayan kar rahe they unki qaum walon ne unko itna maara ke lahu-luhaan kar diya wo apne munh se khoon poonchhtey they aur yun dua kartey jaateyرب اغفر لقومي، Mina فإنهم لا يعلمون ''parwardigaar meri qaum walon ko bakhsh de wo naadaan hain.''
6930,"jab main tum se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki koi hadis bayan karun to qism Allah ki agar main aasman se nichey gir padoon ye mujh ko us se achchha lagta hai ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jhoot baandhon. haan jab mujh main tum mein aapas mein guftgu ho to usmein bana kar baat kehney mein koi burai nahi. kyonke (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai) ladai tadbeer aur makar ka naam hai. dekho maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke akheer zamana qareeb hai jab aisey log musalmaanon mein niklengey jo naii-umr ke bewaqoof hongey (unki aql mein futoor hoga) zahir main to saari makhlooq ke kalaamon mein jo behtar hai (yani hadis shareef) wo padhengey magar dar-haqiqat eman ka noor unke halaq se nichey nahi utrey ga, wo Deen se is tarah bahar ho jaeinge jaisey teer shikar ke janwar se paar nikal jata hai. (is mein kuchh laga nahi rahtaa) tum un logon ko jahan paanaa bina hichkichaahat qatl karna. unko jahan paogey qatl karne mein qiyamat ke din sawab milega."
6931,wo donon abu-Saeed-khudrii (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse puchha kya tum ne harooriyya ke barey mein kuchh Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai? unhon-ne kaha harooriyya to main janta nahi magar maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke is ummat main aur yun nahi farmaya is ummat mein se kuchh log aisey paida hongey ke tum apni Namaz ko unki Namaz ke samney haqeer jano gey aur Quran ki tilawat bhi karengey magar Quran unke halqon se nichey nahi utrey ga. wo Deen se is tarah nikal jaeinge jaisey teer janwar mein se paar nikal jata hai aur phir teer phainkney wala apne teer ko dekhta hai iske baad jad mein (jo kamaan se lagi rehti hai) usko shak hota hai shayad usmein khoon laga ho magar wo bhi saaf .
6932,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke wo Islam se is tarah bahar ho jaeinge jis tarah teer kamaan se bahar ho jata hai.
6933,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) taqseem farma rahe they ke Abdullaah-bin-ziil-khuweysiraa (الخویصرہ) tamimi aaya aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! insaf keejiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke afsos agar main insaf nahi karunga to aur kon karega . is par Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey ijazat dijiye ke main uski gardan mar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi iske kuchh aisey sathi hongey ke unki Namaz aur rozey ke samney tum apni Namaz aur rozey ko haqeer samjho gey lekin wo Deen se is tarah bahar ho jaeinge jis tarah teer janwar mein se bahar nikal jata hai. teer ke par ko dekha jaey lekin is par koi nishan nahi, phir us paikaan (teer ya teer ki nok) ko dekha jaey aur wahan bhi koi nishan nahi, phir iske baad ko dekha jaey aur yahan bhi koi nishan nahi, phir uski lakdi ko dekha jaey aur wahan bhi koi nishan nahi kyonke wo ( janwar ke jism se teer chalaayaa gaya tha) leed, gaubar aur khoon sabse aagey (be-daagh) nikal gaya (isii tarah wo log Islam se saaf nikal jaaeinge) unki nishani aik mard hoga jiska aik hath aurat ki chhaatii ki tarah ya yun farmaya ke gosht ke thal-thal (تھل تھل) kartey lothdey ki tarah hoga. ye log musalmaanon mein phoot ke zamane mein paida hongey. abu-Saeed-khudrii (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke maine ye hadis Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai aur main gawahi deta hun ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne naharwaan mein unse jang ki thi aur main us jang mein unke sath tha aur unke paas un logon ke aik shakhs ko qaidi bana kar laya gaya to usmein wahi tamam cheezein thin jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan farmai thin. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Quran Majeed ki ye aayat nazil hui (ومنهم من يلمزك في الصدقات‏) ke ''unmein se kuchh wo hain jo aap ke sadqey ki taqseem mein aib pakadtey hain.''"
6934,"maine Sahal-bin-Hunaif (badrii sahaabii) (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khawaarij ke silsiley mein kuchh farmatey huey suna hai, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna hai aur aap ne Iraq ki taraf hath se ishara farmaya tha ke idhar se aik jamat nikley gii ye log Quran Majeed padhengey lekin Quran Majeed unke halqon se nichey nahi utrey ga . wo Islam se is tarah bahar ho jaeinge jaisey teer shikar ke janwar se bahar nikal jata hai."
6935,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak do aisey giroh aapas mein jang na karein jinka dawa aik hi ho.''
6936,"maine Hishaam-bin-hakeem ko Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein sura furqan padhtey suna jab ghaur se suna to wo bahut si aisi qiraton ke sath padh rahe they jin se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey nahi padhaayaa tha. qareeb tha ke Namaz hi mein, main un par hamla kar deta lekin maine intizar kya aur jab unhon-ne salam phera to unki chadar se ya (unhon-ne ye kaha ke) apni chadar se maine unki gardan mein phandaa daal diya aur unse puchha ke is tarah tumhen kis ne padhaayaa hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey is tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne padhaayaa hai. maine unse kaha ke jhoot boltey ho, Allah ki qism ye sura mujhey bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne padhai hai jo maine tumhen abhi padhtey suna hai. chunanche main unhein kheenchtaa hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine usey sura furqan aur tarah par padhtey suna hai jis tarah aap ne mujhey nahi padhai thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bhi sura furqan padhai hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke umr ! unhein chhod do. Hisham sura padho . unhon-ne isi tarah padh kar sunaya jis tarah maine unhein padhtey suna tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke isi tarah nazil hui thi phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke umr ! ab tum padho . maine padha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isi tarah nazil hui thi phir farmaya ye Quran saat (7) qiraton mein nazil hua hai isliye tumhen jis tarah aasani ho padho ."
6937,"jab ye aayat nazil hui (الذين آمنوا ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظل‏) ''wo log jo eman ley aaey aur apne eman ke sath zulm ko nahi milaayaa'' to sahaba ko ye mamla bahut mushkil nazar aaya aur unhon-ne kaha ham mein kon hoga jo zulm na karta ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska matlab wo nahi hai jo tum samajhtey ho balke iska matlab luqman (Alaihissalam) ke us irshad mein hai jo unhon-ne apne ladkey se kaha tha (يا بنى لا تشرك بالله إن الشرك لظلم عظيم) ke ''aey betey ! Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraanaa, bila shubah shirk karna bahut bada zulm hai.''"
6938,"subah ke waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey phir aik sahib ne puchha ke Maalik-bin-dukhshun (الدخشن) kahan hain? hamarey qabeele ke aik shakhs ne jawab diya ke wo munafiq hai, Allah aur uske rasool se usey mohabbat nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke kya tum aisa nahi samajhtey ke wo kalima la ilaaha-illallaah ka iqrar karta hai aur uska maqsad us se Allah ki raza hai. us sahabi ne kaha ke haan, ye to hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir jo banda bhi qiyamat ke din us kalima ko lekar aayega, Allah Taala is par jahannam ko haram kar dega."
6939,"abu-Abdur-Rehman aur Hibban bin Atiya ka aapas mein ikhtilaf hua. abu-Abdur-Rehman ne Hibban se kaha ke aapko malum hai ke aap ke sathi khoon bahaney mein kis qadr jari ho gaey hain. unka ishara Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha. is par Hibban ne kaha unhon-ne kya kiya hai, tera bap nahi. abu-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke mujhey, Zuber aur Abu-Marsad (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bheja aur ham sab ghodon par Sawar they Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao aur jab rauza khaakh par pahuncho (jo Madina se baara meel ke faasle par aik jagah hai) abu-Salma ne bayan kya ke abu-Awana ne khaakh ke badley haaj kaha hai. to wahan tumhen aik aurat (saara naamii) milegii aur uske paas Haatib bin abi Balta' ka aik khat hai jo mushrekeene-Makka ko likha gaya hai tum wo khat mere paas laao. chunanche ham apne ghodon par daudey aur ham ne usey wahin pakda jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya tha. wo aurat apne oont par Sawar ja rahi thi Haatib-bin-abii-Balta' (Raziallahu anhu) ne ahal Makka ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Makka ko aaney ki khabar di thi. ham ne us aurat se kaha ke tumharey paas wo khat kahan hai usne kaha ke mere paas to koi khat nahi hai ham ne iska oont bitha diya aur uske kajaawa ki talashi li lekin usmein koi khat nahi mila. mere sathi ne kaha ke uske paas koi khat nahi malum hota. rawi ne bayan kya ke hamein yaqin hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghalat baat nahi farmai phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne qism khaaii ke us zaat ki qism jiski qism khaaii jati hai khat nikal de warna mein tujhey nangii karunga ab wo aurat apne nefey ki taraf jhukii us ne aik chadar kamar par baandh rakhi thi aur khat nikala . iske baad ye log khat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! us ne Allah aur uske rasool aur musalmanon ke sath khayanat ki hai, mujhey ijazat dijiye ke main uski gardan mar dun. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Haatib ! tum ne aisa kyon kiya? Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! bhala kya mujh se ye mumkin hai ke main Allah aur uske rasool par eman na rakhoon mera matlab us khat ke likhney se sirf ye tha ke mera aik ehsan Makka walon par ho jaey jiski wjah se main apni jaaidaad aur baal bachchon ko (unke hath se) bacha loon. baat ye hai ke aap ke ashaab mein koi aisa nahi jiske Makka mein unki qaum mein ke aisey log na hon jiski wjah se Allah unke bachchon aur jaaidaad par koi aafat nahi aaney deta. magar mera wahan koi nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Haatib ne sach kaha hai. bhalai ke siwa unke barey mein aur kuchh na kaho. bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne dobara kaha ke ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us ne Allah aur uske rasool aur mominon ke sath khayanat ki hai. mujhey ijazat dijiye ke main uski gardan mar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya ye jange-badr mein Sharik honey walon mein se nahi hain? tumhen kya malum Allah Taala unke aamaal ko janta tha aur phir farmaya ke jo chaho karo maine jannat tumharey liye likh di hai is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aankhon main ( khushi se) aansu bhar aaey aur arz kya : Allah aur uske rasool hi ko haqiqat ka zyada ilm hai. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke) khaakh ( zyada sahi hai lekin abu-Awana ne (haaj) hi bayan kya hai aur lafz (haaj) badla hua hai ye aik jagah ka naam hai aur Hushaim ne ( khaakh ( bayan kya hai."
